OL,3,CTiger Woods involved in car crash in
OL,4,CFlorida
OL,6,FTiger Woods was involved in a rollover
OL,7,Fcar crash on Friday, the Martin County
OL,8,FSheriff's Office has told media
OL,9,Foutlets.
OL,11,FAuthorities say the rollover crash
OL,12,Foccurred just after 2 pm local time
OL,13,F(around 7pm UK time), not far from
OL,14,Fwhere Woods lives in Jupiter Island,
OL,15,FFlorida. There were no other details,
OL,16,Fthough CBS 12 cited a source as saying
OL,17,Fthere were no serious injuries.
OL,19,FWoods' manager at Excel Sports did not
OL,20,Fimmediately respond to a text seeking
OL,21,Finformation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
