OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774850710
OL,3,CTiger Woods involved in car crash in
OL,4,CFlorida
OL,6,FIt is the third time Woods has been
OL,7,Finvolved in a car crash, most recently
OL,8,Fin February 2021 when his SUV ran off
OL,9,Fa coastal road in Los Angeles at high
OL,10,Fspeed, which led to multiple leg and
OL,11,Fankle injuries. Woods said later
OL,12,Fdoctors considered amputation.
OL,14,FThe 50-year-old is currently on the
OL,15,Fgolf comeback trail after rupturing
OL,16,Fhis Achilles just over a year ago and
OL,17,Fthen undergoing his seventh back
OL,18,Fsurgery late last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
